└── PLATFORM.mdf                      # ← this document
```

**Roles (4-tier RBAC).**

| Role | Reach |
|---|---|
| Admin | Everything: users, currencies (write), pricing-config lifecycle, dev-reset, all transitions and exports |
| Manager | Shipments + packages + master data + transitions + exports + WhatsApp + customer messaging. Cannot manage users or write currencies. |
| Accountant | Read-only for shipments/packages, can override pricing, can run exports + WhatsApp |
| Field | Warehouse floor: package transitions limited to `receive`, `pack`, `ready-to-ship` (per `FIELD_PKG_TRANSITIONS`). Can upload photos. |

