## 2. Domain Model

### 2.1 Entity catalog

21 entities. One file per entity in `backend/ShippingPlatform.Api/Models/Entities/`.

| Entity | Key fields | Notable | FK behavior |
|---|---|---|---|
| `AdminUser` | Email, PasswordHash (BCrypt), IsActive, **Role**, LastLoginAt | Unique index on `Email`. `Role` added in `AddUserRole` migration. | — |
| `Customer` | Name, PrimaryPhone, Email?, CompanyName?, TaxId?, BillingAddress?, IsActive | 1:1 `WhatsAppConsent` (cascade delete). Indexes on Email + PrimaryPhone. | — |
| `WhatsAppConsent` | CustomerId (PK + FK), OptInStatusUpdates, OptInDeparturePhotos, OptInArrivalPhotos, OptedOutAt? | Auto-created with customer on seed. | Cascade from Customer |
| `Warehouse` | Code (unique, ≤3), Name, City, Country, MaxWeightKg(10,3), MaxCbm(10,3), IsActive | 4 seeded: BEI, GAB, CHN, DXB | — |
| `GoodType` | NameEn, NameAr, CanBreak, CanBurn, IsActive | Bilingual labels (Arabic field unused on FE — see §9.19) | — |
| `PricingConfig` | Name, Currency(≤3), EffectiveFrom, EffectiveTo?, DefaultRatePerKg(12,4), DefaultRatePerCbm(12,4), MinimumCharge(12,4), Status | Status = Draft → Scheduled → Active → Retired | — |
| `Shipment` | RefCode (unique), TiiuCode(≤11), OriginWarehouseId, DestinationWarehouseId, Status, MaxWeightKg(10,3), MaxCbm(10,3), TotalWeightKg(10,3), TotalCbm(10,3), PlannedDepartureDate, PlannedArrivalDate, ActualDepartureAt?, ActualArrivalAt?, External\* tracking, **InvoiceNumber?, InvoiceYear?**, CreatedAt | New invoice fields pinned on first commercial-documents export. Status, PlannedDepartureDate indexed. | OriginWarehouse/DestinationWarehouse: **Restrict** |
| `ShipmentSequence` | OriginWarehouseCode, Year, LastNumber | RefCode format `{Code}-{YY}{NN}`. Unique index `(OriginWarehouseCode, Year)`. Optimistic concurrency (see §9.6). | — |
| `Package` | ShipmentId, CustomerId, ProvisionMethod, Status, WeightKg(10,3), Cbm(10,3), Currency(≤3), AppliedRatePerKg(12,4), AppliedRatePerCbm(12,4), ChargeAmount(18,2), HasDeparturePhotos, HasArrivalPhotos, HasPricingOverride, SupplyOrderId?, Note(≤1000), CreatedAt | `Currency` is currently semantically dead (see §9.8). Status, SupplyOrderId, ShipmentId, CustomerId indexed. | Customer/Shipment: **Restrict** |
| `PackageItem` | PackageId, GoodTypeId, Quantity (default 1), **Unit (default Box)**, **UnitPrice?(18,2)**, Note(≤500) | `Unit` and `UnitPrice` added 2026-05-01. `UnitPrice` always USD (see §9.8). | Cascade from Package |
| `PackagePricingOverride` | PackageId, OverrideType, OriginalValue(18,2), NewValue(18,2), Reason(≤500), AdminUserId, CreatedAt | Three override types (RatePerKg/RatePerCbm/TotalCharge). Indexed on PackageId. | Cascade from Package |
| `Supplier` | Name(≤200), Email?(≤200), IsActive | For procurement | — |
| `SupplyOrder` | CustomerId, SupplierId, PackageId?, Name(≤200), PurchasePrice(18,2), Details?(≤2000), Status, CancelReason?(≤500) | Unique index on PackageId. Lifecycle: Draft→Approved→Ordered→DeliveredToWarehouse→PackedIntoPackage→Closed. | Customer/Supplier: **Restrict** |
| `Media` | PackageId, Stage, BlobKey(≤500), PublicUrl(≤500), Notes?(≤1000), CapturedAt?, UploadedAt, RecordedByAdminUserId, OperatorName?(≤200) | Stages: Receiving/Departure/Arrival/Other. Watermarked on upload. `RecordedByAdminUserId` field exists but never populated (§9.14). | Cascade from Package |
| `WhatsAppCampaign` | Type, ShipmentId, TriggeredByAdminUserId, RecipientCount, Completed, CreatedAt | Three campaign types (StatusUpdate/Departure/Arrival photos) | — |
| `WhatsAppDeliveryLog` | CampaignId, CustomerId, Phone(≤30), Result, FailureReason?(≤500), SentAt? | Result = Pending/Sent/Failed/SkippedNoOptIn. Pending rows don't flip async (§9.15). | Cascade from Campaign |
| `AuditLog` | EntityType, EntityId, Action, OldValue(≤2000), NewValue(≤2000), AdminUserId?, CreatedAt | Indexed on (EntityType, EntityId), AdminUserId, CreatedAt. **Sparsely populated** (§9.13). | — |
| **`Currency`** | Code (unique, ≤3), Name(≤60), Symbol?(≤8), IsBase, AnchorCurrencyCode?(≤3), Rate?(18,8), IsActive, UpdatedAt | New 2026-05-01. Anchored chain (see §3.4). | — |
| **`ShipmentRateSnapshot`** | ShipmentId, Event (Departed/Arrived/Manual), CurrencyCode(≤3), RateToBase(18,8), CapturedAt | New 2026-05-01. Composite unique `(ShipmentId, Event, CurrencyCode)`. | Cascade from Shipment |
| **`InvoiceSequence`** | Year (unique), LastNumber | New 2026-05-01. Year-scoped invoice counter. Optimistic concurrency (§9.6). | — |

