### 2.3 Decimal precision matrix

Configured in [`AppDbContext.OnModelCreating`](backend/ShippingPlatform.Api/Data/AppDbContext.cs).

| Domain | Precision | Fields |
|---|---|---|
| Weight (kg) / Volume (CBM) | (10, 3) | `Package.WeightKg`/`Cbm`, `Shipment.MaxWeightKg`/`MaxCbm`/`TotalWeightKg`/`TotalCbm`, `Warehouse.MaxWeightKg`/`MaxCbm` |
| Pricing rates | (12, 4) | `Package.AppliedRatePerKg`/`AppliedRatePerCbm`, `PricingConfig.DefaultRatePerKg`/`DefaultRatePerCbm`/`MinimumCharge` |
| Money amounts | (18, 2) | `Package.ChargeAmount`, `PackageItem.UnitPrice`, `PackagePricingOverride.OriginalValue`/`NewValue`, `SupplyOrder.PurchasePrice` |
