### 2.4 Cascade behavior

Configured explicitly in `OnModelCreating`.

| FK | Behavior | Why |
|---|---|---|
| Shipment → OriginWarehouse / DestinationWarehouse | Restrict | Prevent accidental warehouse delete from blowing away history |
| Package → Customer / Shipment | Restrict | Keep package history if customer/shipment deactivates |
| SupplyOrder → Customer / Supplier | Restrict | Same reasoning |
| PackageItem → Package | Cascade | Items are owned by their package |
| Media → Package | Cascade | Photos die with their package |
| PackagePricingOverride → Package | Cascade | Audit trail tied to package |
| WhatsAppDeliveryLog → Campaign | Cascade | Logs are owned by their campaign |
| WhatsAppConsent → Customer | Cascade | 1:1 owned record |
| ShipmentRateSnapshot → Shipment | Cascade | Snapshots are tied to their shipment |

