## 4. API Surface

Auth model: every controller is gated by `MapControllers().RequireAuthorization()` ([`Program.cs:93`](backend/ShippingPlatform.Api/Program.cs#L93)) except endpoints with explicit `[AllowAnonymous]`. Method-level `[Authorize(Roles="...")]` further restricts mutating endpoints. JWT (HS256, 8h, claims: nameidentifier/email/role) is sent in `Authorization: Bearer ...`.

### 4.1 Endpoint catalog

**`AuthController`** (`/api/auth`) — rate-limited 10/min on `login`.

| Verb | Path | Roles | Purpose |
|---|---|---|---|
| POST | `/login` | Anonymous | Returns `{ token, email, role }` |

**`UsersController`** (`/api/users`)

| Verb | Path | Roles | Purpose |
|---|---|---|---|
| GET | `/users` | Admin, Manager | List users |
| GET | `/users/{id}` | Admin, Manager | Single user |
| POST | `/users` | Admin | Create user |
| PUT | `/users/{id}` | Admin | Update user (role, isActive) |

**`CustomerController`** (`/api/customers`)

| Verb | Path | Roles | Purpose |
|---|---|---|---|
| GET | `/customers` | Admin, Manager, Accountant | Optional `?q=` search; **no pagination** (§9.25) |
| GET | `/customers/{id}` | Admin, Manager, Accountant | Single |
| POST | `/customers` | Admin, Manager | Create |
| PUT | `/customers/{id}` | Admin, Manager | Update |
| GET | `/customers/{id}/packages` | Authenticated | Customer history |
| PATCH | `/customers/{id}/whatsapp-consent` | Admin, Manager | Toggle opt-in flags |
| POST | `/customers/{customerId}/whatsapp/status?shipmentId=` | Admin, Manager | Single-customer status WhatsApp |
| POST | `/customers/{customerId}/whatsapp/photos/departure?shipmentId=` | Admin, Manager | Single-customer departure photos |
| POST | `/customers/{customerId}/whatsapp/photos/arrival?shipmentId=` | Admin, Manager | Single-customer arrival photos |

**`WarehouseController`** (`/api/warehouses`) — GET, GET/{id} authenticated; POST/PUT Admin/Manager.

**`GoodTypeController`** (`/api/good-types`) — same pattern.

**`SupplierController`** (`/api/suppliers`) — same pattern.

**`PricingConfigController`** (`/api/pricing-configs`)

| Verb | Path | Roles | Purpose |
|---|---|---|---|
| GET / GET{id} | | Authenticated | Read |
| POST / PUT | | Admin, Manager | Create/update |
| POST | `/{id}/activate` | Admin, Manager | Sets this config Active, retires all others |
| POST | `/{id}/retire` | Admin, Manager | Retire |

**`ShipmentsController`** (`/api/shipments`)

| Verb | Path | Roles | Purpose |
|---|---|---|---|
| GET | `/shipments` | Authenticated | Paginated list with `?status=`, `?q=`, `?dateFrom=`, `?dateTo=`, `?page=`, `?pageSize=` |
| GET | `/shipments/{id}` | Authenticated | Single |
| POST | `/shipments` | Admin, Manager | Create |
| PATCH | `/shipments/{id}` | Admin, Manager | Update planned dates / TIIU |
| POST | `/{id}/schedule` | Admin, Manager | Draft → Scheduled (TIIU required) |
| POST | `/{id}/ready-to-depart` | Admin, Manager | Scheduled → ReadyToDepart |
| POST | `/{id}/depart` *(or `/ship`)* | Admin, Manager | ReadyToDepart → Departed (gate + FX snapshot) |
| POST | `/{id}/arrive` | Admin, Manager | Departed → Arrived (FX snapshot) |
| POST | `/{id}/close` *(or `/complete`)* | Admin, Manager | Arrived → Closed (gate) |
| POST | `/{id}/cancel` | Admin, Manager | Cancel from Draft/Scheduled |
| POST | `/{id}/tracking/sync` | Admin, Manager | Maersk sync |
| GET | `/{id}/audit-log` | Authenticated *(see §9.5)* | History |
| GET | `/{id}/media` | Authenticated | Media attached to packages |
| GET | `/{id}/ready-to-depart/preview` | Authenticated | Shows which packages depart vs reassign |
| POST | `/{shipmentId}/packages/bulk-transition` | Admin, Manager | Validate-then-execute bulk transition |
| GET | `/{id}/fx-snapshots` | Authenticated | All snapshots for this shipment |
| PUT | `/{id}/fx-snapshots/{currencyCode}` | Admin, Manager | Upsert Manual override |
| DELETE | `/{id}/fx-snapshots/{currencyCode}` | Admin, Manager | Remove Manual override |

