| GET | `/api/packages/{id}` | Authenticated | Detail (with items + media) |
| PATCH | `/api/packages/{id}` | Admin, Manager, Field | Update weight/cbm/note |
| POST | `/api/packages/{id}/receive` *(and pack/ready-to-ship/cancel)* | Admin, Manager, Field | Field-permitted transitions |
| POST | `/api/packages/{id}/ship` *(and arrive-destination/ready-for-handout/handout)* | Admin, Manager | Manager-only transitions; ship + handout enforce photo gates |
| POST | `/api/packages/{id}/items` | Admin, Manager, Field | Add item (Unit + UnitPrice) |
| PUT | `/api/packages/{id}/items/{itemId}` | Admin, Manager, Field | Update item |
| DELETE | `/api/packages/{id}/items/{itemId}` | Admin, Manager, Field | Remove item |
