| DELETE | `/currencies/{code}` | Admin | Delete (refuses if base or referenced as anchor) |

**`DevController`** (`/api/dev`) — `[Authorize(Roles="Admin")]` + `IWebHostEnvironment.IsDevelopment()` guard.

| Verb | Path | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| POST | `/dev/reset-data` | Wipe transactional tables, reseed customers + currencies. 404 if not Development. |

### 4.2 Authentication

`POST /api/auth/login` body `{ email, password }` → `{ token, email, role }`. Token is HS256 with 8-hour expiry, signed by `Auth:Secret` (see §9.1 for the fallback security risk). Claims: `nameidentifier` (user id), `emailaddress`, `role`. No refresh token, no lockout, no password reset — see §9.4.

### 4.3 DTOs

All in [`Dtos/ApiDtos.cs`](backend/ShippingPlatform.Api/Dtos/ApiDtos.cs). New (May 2026): `LookupItemDto`, `CurrencyDto`, `UpsertCurrencyRequest`, `ShipmentRateSnapshotDto`, `UpsertManualRateRequest`, `CommercialDocumentsRequest`. `PackageItemDto` extended with `Unit`/`UnitPrice`. `DtoMap` extension methods (`ToDto`) handle every entity-to-DTO conversion.

