| Spec | Coverage |
|---|---|
| `auth.spec.ts` | Login/logout, error toasts, anon redirect |
| `dashboard.spec.ts` | Counters render, navigation buttons |
| `navigation.spec.ts` | Sidebar + command palette |
| `master-data.spec.ts` | Warehouses + good types CRUD |
| `customers.spec.ts` | CRUD + WhatsApp consent |
| `packages.spec.ts` | Items, photos, transitions |
| `shipments.spec.ts` | Filtering, create, transitions, TIIU edit |
| `pricing.spec.ts` | Configs CRUD, activate/retire, override |
| `supply-orders.spec.ts` | CRUD + lifecycle, cancel reason |
| `users.spec.ts` | CRUD, role checks, last-admin guard, Manager-cannot-create-users, Field-cannot-see-Customers |
| **`zz-manager-full-flow.spec.ts`** | Complete Manager-driven flow: reset → 5 customers → supplier → shipment → 4 direct + 1 indirect package → all transitions → photo uploads → close shipment |

**No backend test project exists.** No tests cover the new Currencies CRUD, FX Snapshots section, Unit/UnitPrice fields, or the Commercial Invoice + Packing List export — see §9.26.

Running: `cd frontend && npx playwright test`. The full suite runs in ~3–5 minutes against a live backend on `http://localhost:51295` (IIS Express) and Vite on `http://localhost:5173`.

