## Appendix — File-path quick reference

| What | Where |
|---|---|
| Entity classes | `backend/ShippingPlatform.Api/Models/Entities/*.cs` |
| Enums | `backend/ShippingPlatform.Api/Models/Enums.cs` |
| DbContext + indexes/cascades | `backend/ShippingPlatform.Api/Data/AppDbContext.cs` |
| DTOs + DtoMap | `backend/ShippingPlatform.Api/Dtos/ApiDtos.cs` |
| Validators | `backend/ShippingPlatform.Api/Validators/RequestValidators.cs` |
| Core services | `backend/ShippingPlatform.Api/Services/Services.cs` (token, blob, refcode, pricing, capacity, photocompliance, watermark, twilio, audit, transitionrules) |
| FX services | `backend/ShippingPlatform.Api/Services/Currency/*.cs` (namespace `Services.FxRates`) |
| Export builders | `backend/ShippingPlatform.Api/Services/Exports/*.cs` |
| Seed | `backend/ShippingPlatform.Api/Services/SeedHelper.cs` |
| Business layer | `backend/ShippingPlatform.Api/Business/*.cs` |
| Controllers | `backend/ShippingPlatform.Api/Controllers/*.cs` |
| FE entry | `frontend/src/main.tsx`, `App.tsx`, `Portal.tsx`, `Protected.tsx` |
| FE RBAC | `frontend/src/helpers/rbac.ts` |
| FE pages | `frontend/src/pages/*` |
| FE shared components | `frontend/src/components/*` |
| FE API client | `frontend/src/api/*.ts` |
| E2E tests | `frontend/e2e/*.spec.ts` |
